END IF
========

Control flow statement for conditional branching.

Syntax:

If expression Then [statement(s)] [Else [statement(s)]] [End If]
or
If expression Then : [statement(s)] [Else [statement(s)]] : End If
or
If expression Then
	[statement(s)]
[ Elseif expression Then ]
	[statement(s)]
[ Else ]
	[statement(s)]
End If

Remark: `EndIf` (without blank) is also supported like in QB for backward
compatibility.

